212
00:18:55,280 --> 00:18:56,280
Just remember,

213
00:18:58,680 --> 00:19:00,440
you are an ordinary person.

214
00:19:01,800 --> 00:19:03,440
But you are pure and clean.

215
00:19:05,800 --> 00:19:06,520
In the future,

216
00:19:07,920 --> 00:19:10,040
you still have many, many good days ahead.

217
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:16,080
You must live well.

218
00:19:26,720 --> 00:19:27,520
Be good.

219
00:19:33,680 --> 00:19:34,920
Mom loves you.

220
00:19:55,040 --> 00:19:55,840
At that time,

221
00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:58,960
it was the hateful me who returned.

222
00:20:02,040 --> 00:20:03,320
My sister

223
00:20:05,080 --> 00:20:07,560
never really existed.

224
00:20:12,440 --> 00:20:14,400
You imagined a sister in your mind.

225
00:20:15,920 --> 00:20:17,560
A sister who wanted revenge.

226
00:20:21,560 --> 00:20:23,440
The sister I always hated

227
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:29,000
was just another version of myself I didn't want to face.
